data.description: Subject to cancellation of existing escrow. Located in the peaceful Suncrest Villas East, this charming, remodeled townhome exudes comfort and convenience. Offering 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a 1-car garage. Discover a semi-open layout that effortlessly connects the living & dining areas, ideal for both hosting guests and daily ease! Abundant natural light, neutral palette, and wood-look tile flooring t/out enhance the inviting ambiance. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, granite counters, recessed lighting, and white shaker cabinetry w/crown molding. One of the bedrooms features two closets, providing ample storage. Check out the backyard with a covered patio for relaxing after a busy day!, Enough room to add your perfect outdoor living space.. Move in ready,
